name: Hennessy & Sons Original Harris Tweed Silver Grey
description:
This exclusive item is handcrafted with the famous original Harris Tweed wool and uses French anti-allergic Alsavel lining.

Harris Tweed Wool has been hand woven by the islanders of Lewis, Harris, Uist and Barra in their homes, using pure virgin wool that has been dyed and spun in the Outer Hebrides.

This is the definition of Harris Tweed contained in the Harris Tweed Act of 1993 and it ensures that all products certified with the Harris Tweed Orb symbol complies with this definition and is genuine Harris Tweed, the world’s only commercially produced hand woven tweed.

 All metal components are in high quality 316L Stainless Steel to guarantee a strong hold of your beloved companion.
